snippet.title: Michael and Amber Have an Explosive Chat | Love Island 2019
snippet.description:
Michael's head has completely turned since Amber's been away at Casa Amor. Our fireman decided to follow his heart and recouple, whilst Amber made her way back into the villa a single lady. Tension floods the atmosphere as Michael and Amber finally have a very awkward conversation.
